OL,3,CTeen banned from Dixy Chicken shop and
OL,4,C'ordered to behave' in Worcester
OL,6,FA nuisance Worcester teenager has been
OL,7,Fbanned from a Dixy Chicken shop and a
OL,8,FTesco Express as well as being
OL,9,F"ordered to behave" in the city centre
OL,10,Ffor three years.
OL,12,FSam White, of no fixed abode, was
OL,13,Fgiven a Criminal Behaviour Order (CBO)
OL,14,Fat Worcester Magistrates Court on
OL,15,FThursday (3 October).
OL,17,FIt follows convictions for thefts
OL,18,Fwithin Worcester city centre,
OL,19,Fincluding Tesco Express, in Foregate
OL,20,FStreet.
