OL,3,CTeen banned from Dixy Chicken shop and
OL,4,C'ordered to behave' in Worcester
OL,6,FThe court also heard the 19-year-old
OL,7,Fbehaved in a disorderly manner, being
OL,8,Fabusive, threatening to shop staff and
OL,9,Fcausing significant alarm and fear to
OL,10,Fmembers of the public.
OL,12,FWhite was handed the CBO for three
OL,13,Fyears, which prohibits him from
OL,14,Fentering Tesco Express, Foregate
OL,15,FStreet, Worcester, or being in the
OL,16,Farea directly outside as defined in a
OL,17,Fmapped area.
