OL,6,FIt also stops him Entering Dixy
OL,7,FChicken, in Comberton Hill,
OL,8,FKidderminster or entering Co-op, in
OL,9,FWorcester Road, in Malvern.
OL,11,FIt also prohibits him from refusing to
OL,12,Fleave an area or premises when asked
OL,13,Fby someone who has authority to do so,
OL,14,For behaving in a manner that causes a
OL,15,Fnuisance in the community within
OL,16,FWorcester city centre.
