OL,6,FPolice Sergeant Sarah England, of
OL,7,FWorcester city centre team, said: "We
OL,8,Fare pleased the court has granted a
OL,9,FCBO against White whose antisocial
OL,10,Fbehaviour and thefts have impacted
OL,11,Fshops and businesses in the city and
OL,12,Ffurther afield, and caused alarm and
OL,13,Fdistress to members of the public.
OL,15,F"Anyone who sees White breaching the
OL,16,Fterms of his CBO should report it to
OL,17,Fus."
